posting_body: ['REF# 11R68', '$4500 · 4/2.5 · Aventura · Unfurnished · Via Venture Neighborhood · 1920 Sqft', 'Call ➟ Text ➟ WhatsApp', "📲 786'*'5O5'*'4314", 'Carlos Manchego', 'Goldstein Realty', 'show contact info', "Beautiful 4 Bedrooms 2 ½ Baths two story townhouse located in Lennar's Las Ramblas Via Ventura gated community.", 'Easy access to major highways, just 2 miles west of I-95 and minutes away from Aventura Mall, Hallandale Beach, and Hard Rock Casino.', 'Open floor concept w/ tiled first floor, carpet throughout the 2nd floor, all bedrooms are located on the 2nd floor.', 'Master Bedroom w/ shower and double vanity.', 'Camara system is optional and up to tenant to pay monthly service.', 'The private back patio with a wooden privacy fence is perfect for relaxing evening.', 'There is also an attached 1 car garage with 2 extra spaces outside driveway.', 'Great Club House with Fantastic pool, Gym, Playground for kids.', 'Read Less', 'REF# 11R68', 'tags:', 'canvas condo, centro lofts, cynergi, solaris at brickell, cynergi, brickell ten condo, brickell bay tower, infinity, brickell shores, the loft ii, parc lofts, the ivy, costa bella, the vue at brickell, brickell on the river, 1060 brickell, krystal tower, bay house, grovenor house, baltus house, coconut grove bayshore condo, ocean view, courts brickell key, biscayne beach, marina blue, villas de vizcaya homes, the bond, the vue at brickell condo, vizcayne south, brickell key two, holleman park homes, morningside homes,, parc lofts, fortune house', '_mr11']
